      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it runs like a dream and looks great too. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
