    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example retains its mechanical integrity with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the 50/50 weight distribution as intended. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear torque and that signature metallic rasp. A true enthusiast's specimen ready for the canyon or the track.",
      "price": 34500.0,
