    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-loved daily driver that has been maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Slate Grey Metallic; while the paint retains a high-gloss luster, there are minor, typical stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort. The black leather upholstery is free of punctures or tears, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display\u2014from the heated seats to the navigation system\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak form. It has a comprehensive service history, including a recent major interval service where the spark plugs, filters, and fluids were replaced. The engine idle is whisper-quiet, and the transmission delivers crisp, confident shifts. The tires are matching Michelin Pilot Sports with approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes provide firm, immediate stopping power. This car offers a turn-key experience for a buyer looking for a reliable, premium vehicle that has many miles of enjoyment left to give.",
